pageTitle: CCHS 4x400 team wins first in home track meet | MyCarrollNews.com
TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {33096=Copyright © 2015, 19117=The Panthers 4x400 meter relay team, made up of senior Evan Mefford, sophomore Michael Burns, sophomore Taylor Byrd and senior Devin Gray, finished in first place with a time of 3:48.24 at Carroll County’s All Comers meet on Tuesday, March 13.
